The electronic assistants had almost nothing to do on the entire track; and that even though we found ice at dawn and roll-splitting in the morning at some of these curves.
To sum up, it is an ultra-light car, a car with which you have an indescribable driving pleasure, as it is usually rather rare and in it there is much more than just a small improvement of the Boxster Ss.
